Headline: Baila Night 2016
News Content: Baila Night, the Signature Club Service project organized by the Rotaract Clubs of University of Colombo, Faculty of Arts and Cinnamon Gardens was held on 4th of November at Havelock City Club House for the 5th consecutive time successfully!Photographer - Sujan JayasinghePhotos Credits Goes to - LetMeKnow.lk
